room_title: Escape room "Cabin Heist" by Mission 57 in Salinas
room_address: 711 Cannery Row Suite N Monterey, CA 93940
room_description:
You and your team are in a wood cabin. Your mission is to confiscate all of the cash found on the property, but there's something else. There have been reports that the AI Called Joan is storing her hard drives there. So far no one has been able to find them.

The recon team went in and all they were able to find was the word "Blackbird".  What is it? Who is it? Is it related to the drives?  Sign up for the mission and find out.
